<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Email Template</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    body {
      background: #e6e6e6;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      width: 100% !important;
    }
    .email-container {
      background: #fff;
      width: 100% !important;
      max-width: 480px;
      margin: 0 auto !important;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 0;
      box-shadow: none;
      padding: 0;
      min-height: 80vh;
    }
    .email-header {
      color: #2196f3;
      font-size: 14px;
      padding: 16px 0 0 16px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .email-content {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 24px 32px 16px 32px;
      border-radius: 0;
      background: #fff;
    }
    .logo {
      display: block;
      margin: 0 auto 16px auto;
      width: 180px;
      height: 40px;
      background: url('https://dummyimage.com/180x40/cccccc/000000&text=Logoipsum') no-repeat center center;
      background-size: contain;
    }
    .main-title {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      color: #222;
    }
    .congrats {
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      color: #222;
    }
    .email-body {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #66ffff;
      color: #000;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 500;
      padding: 10px 28px;
      border-radius: 22px;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      margin-top: 8px;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    .note {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #888;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .system-message {
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #aaa;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .regards {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #222;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    .team {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #222;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .email-footer {
      margin-top: 32px;
      padding: 16px 0 0 0;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
    }
    .footer-logo {
      width: 120px;
      height: 24px;
      background-size: contain;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .copyright {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #aaa;
    }
    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
      .email-container {
        width: 100% !important;
        max-width: 100% !important;
        margin: 0 !important;
        border: none !important;
        border-radius: 0 !important;
        box-shadow: none !important;
      }
      .email-content {
        margin: 0 !important;
        padding: 16px 4vw 8px 4vw !important;
      }
      .main-title {
        font-size: 17px !important;
        margin-bottom: 16px !important;
      }
      .congrats, .regards, .team {
        font-size: 13px !important;
      }
      .email-body {
        font-size: 13px !important;
      }
      .cta-button {
        font-size: 13px !important;
        padding: 8px 16px !important;
      }
      .email-footer {
        margin: 0 !important;
        padding: 12px 2vw 0 2vw !important;
      }
      .logo {
        width: 120px !important;
        height: 28px !important;
      }
      .footer-logo {
        width: 80px !important;
        height: 16px !important;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-header">Email Template</div>
  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="email-content">
      <div class="main-title">
      <h1> Truebg</h1>
        Background verification initiated for your role at Truebg.
      </div>
      <div class="congrats">Congratulations, <%= @user_name %>!</div>
      <div class="email-body">
        We're excited to have you join us. Let's complete the final step in the onboarding process.<br>
        This verification is handled by our trusted partner, truebg, and will cover your employment history, educational qualifications, and a criminal record check. Your information will be handled securely and confidentially. Please click the link below to start;
      </div>
      <a href="http://localhost:3000/phone_verification" class="cta-button">Start Secure Verification</a>
      <div class="note">
        This secure link will expire in 7 days. The verification process typically takes 5-10 business days to complete. We will notify you once it’s done and share the details for your first day.
      </div>
      <div class="system-message"> 
        This is a system generated message. Do not reply.
      </div>
      <div class="regards">Best Regards,</div>
      <div class="team">Team Truebg</div>
      <div class="email-footer">
        <div style="font-size:13px; color:#888; margin-bottom:4px;">
          © 2035 Truebg Inc. All rights reserved.
        </div>
        <div style="font-size:12px; color:#888; margin-bottom:4px;">
          Visit us: <a href="https://truebg.com" style="color:#2196f3; text-decoration:none;">Truebg.com</a> |
          Contact: <a href="mailto:support@Truebg.com" style="color:#2196f3; text-decoration:none;">support@Truebg.com</a>
        </div>
        <div style="font-size:11px; color:#aaa;">
          This email and any attachments are confidential and intended solely for the recipient. If you received this in error, please delete it.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>